query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from tag_question AS tq
inner join question AS q
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 0 AND q.score <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('android-pendingintent',
'dbpedia',
'docker-swarm',
'identity',
'jdeveloper',
'lme4',
'mime',
'nsmanagedobjectcontext',
'payment',
'template-specialization',
'uislider',
'variadic-functions',
'vlc',
'xsd-validation');
